        P_MEET_MAXIMINO --> A_FOLLOW_TO_CATS["A: Follow Maximino to Hidden Cat Area"]
        A_FOLLOW_TO_CATS --> O_MAXIMINO_FRIEND["O: Learn Maximino is Key Contact"]
